# IBB Shuttle — Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback routing
#
# RULE: List ONLY known React SPA routes explicitly.
# DO NOT use a wildcard (/* /index.html 200) — that would intercept
# unknown paths like /rus and return HTTP 200 instead of 404,
# violating SEO_LEVEL0_SPEC.md section 8.
#
# Cloudflare Pages serving priority:
#   1. Static files (/{lang}/, /{lang}/pricing/, etc.) — served directly from dist/
#   2. Rules below — only triggered when no static file matches
#   3. 404.html — served with HTTP 404 for all unmatched paths
#
# LANGUAGES: en th zh ja ko ru ar de fr es id hi vi

# ── Language-aware shuttle pages (Level 2 interactive) ──
/en/shuttle    /index.html  200
/th/shuttle    /index.html  200
